[[Cyprus]] was represented by the group [[One (band)|One]] with the song "Gimme". The group was selected internally, so a Cypriot National Final was not held. At the Eurovision Song Contest, the group had a solid result and they qualified Cyprus for the [[Eurovision Song Contest 2003]].

==At Eurovision==
On the night of the final Cyprus performed 1st in the running order, preceding the [[United Kingdom]].  At the close of the voting "Gimme" had received 85 points from 14 countries (the highest being 12 from [[Greece]] and [[Malta]]), placing Cyprus 6th of the 24 entries.  The 12 points from Cyprus were awarded to [[Greece]].

